#: _posts/2024-04-22-ship-cars-leverages-quarkus-to-reach-its-goals.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Comparison of Difficulty/Cost and Ease of Ease-of-Use/Returns Over Time in Adopting Quarkus Features"
